metadata.name: Supernova
metadata.description:
An immersive painting of the cosmos about the creation of a new star "Supernova". Created in virtual reality.  
I was inspired by a photograph from the James Webb Space Telescope showing a fiery hourglass. This is a very exciting sight and this video shows my version of what is happening.

Manifold contract .  
Format: mp4,  
Dimensions: 1280 x 720 px,  
Duration: 1:18.  
Unique Edition 1/1
